Title : Let Curiosity Drive: Fostering Innovation in Data Science
Link : https://multithreaded.stitchfix.com/blog/page/2/
Summary :
- innovation -> born out of curiosity, tinkering
- data scientists can be distracted in a good way
- low cost exploration + risk reducing evidence -> innovation
